br />\n類似係咁"},{"pid":"124d8133b112e1db92df25dc4b0ab04f21a4ff4b","tid":266877,"uid":95475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次都過晒dead line先交</blockquote><br />\n無任何野發生？？<br />\n例如罰款？？"},{"pid":"04f40955919566f7d4ccc4b0619422c9c2ed0fea","tid":266877,"uid":3002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"我試過遲幾日都無咩野喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61c2af49ac5b690322032164e4b3980eae00cf8","tid":266877,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>次次都過晒dead line先交</blockquote><br />\n無任何野發生？？<br />\n例如罰款？？</blockquote><br />\n會再寄多次報稅表畀你，限制之內交，係咁多"},{"pid":"25e2df4ecafc881745b59cf6df294f9627667f4a","tid":266877,"uid":49491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"清左稅係咪再當首次登記？？"},{"pid":"92e75072ba3208b4b3b6c49a60da16b2de2993bc","tid":266877,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"未填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}